# Workday MCP Server HTTP API Tests
# Use with VS Code REST Client extension

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@bearerToken = your_entra_id_bearer_token_here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### List Tools
GET {{baseUrl}}/tools
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### Get Worker Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/tools/call
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

{
  "name": "get_worker",
  "arguments": {
    "auth_token": "{{bearerToken}}"
  }
}

### Get Leave Balances  
POST {{baseUrl}}/tools/call
Content-Type: application/json
