### Search Learning Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/tools/call
Content-Type: application/json  
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

{
  "name": "search_learning_content",
  "arguments": {
    "auth_token": "{{bearerToken}}",
    "query": "compliance"
  }
}

### Book Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/tools/call
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

{
  "name": "book_leave",
  "arguments": {
    "auth_token": "{{bearerToken}}",
    "absence_type_id": "your_absence_type_id",
    "start_date": "2024-12-01",
    "end_date": "2024-12-05",
    "comment": "Personal time off"
  }
}